<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.204.89690.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. A-AD LM valve views of Achnanthidium kangdingnese sp. nov. Scale bar: 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/726840" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.204.89690.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. A-E Achnanthidium kangdingnese sp. nov. SEM external views of raphe valve A, B entire raphe valve C, D valve apex, showing the distal raphe ends E central area of the valve, showing the proximal raphe ends. Scale bars: 2 µm (A, B); 1 µm (C, D); 0.5 µm (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/726841" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.204.89690.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. A-E Achnanthidium kangdingnese sp. nov. SEM internal views of raphe valve A, B entire raphe valve C valve apex, showing the distal raphe ends E central area of the valve, showing the proximal raphe ends D internal areola occluded with fine hymenate structures. Scale bars: 2 µm (A, B); 1 µm (C); 0.5 µm (E); 0.2 µm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/726842" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.204.89690.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. A-D Achnanthidium kangdingnese sp. nov. SEM external views of rapheless valve A, B entire raphe valve C valve apex D central area of the valve. Scale bars: 2 µm (A, B); 1 µm (C); 0.5 µm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/726843" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.204.89690.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. A-C Achnanthidium kangdingnese sp. nov., SEM internal views of rapheless valve A entire raphe valve B central area of the valve C valve apex. Scale bars: 2 µm (A); 0.5 µm (B, C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/726844" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

